rlPoe.name: rlPoe
rlPoe.description: The private MIB module definition for Power Over Ethernet.

rlPethPsePortTable.name: rlPethPsePortTable
rlPethPsePortTable.description: The table listing additional information for Power Over Ethernet ports.

rlPethPsePortGroupIndex.name: rlPethPsePortGroupIndex
rlPethPsePortGroupIndex.description: This variable uniquely identifies the group containing the port to which a power Ethernet PSE is connected. Group means box in the stack, module in a rack and the value 1 MUST be used for non-modular devices. Furthermore, the same value MUST be used in this variable, pethMainPseGroupIndex, and pethNotificationControlGroupIndex to refer to a given box in a stack or module in the rack.

rlPethPsePortIndex.name: rlPethPsePortIndex
rlPethPsePortIndex.description: This variable uniquely identifies the power Ethernet PSE port within group pethPsePortGroupIndex to which the power Ethernet PSE entry is connected.

rlPethPsePortOutputVoltage.name: rlPethPsePortOutputVoltage
rlPethPsePortOutputVoltage.description: This variable indicates on the output voltage level in milli volts from rlPethPsePortIndex.

rlPethPsePortOutputCurrent.name: rlPethPsePortOutputCurrent
rlPethPsePortOutputCurrent.description: This variable indicates on the output current level in milli amper from rlPethPsePortIndex.

rlPethPsePortOutputPower.name: rlPethPsePortOutputPower
rlPethPsePortOutputPower.description: This variable indicates on the output power level in milli watts from rlPethPsePortIndex.

rlPethPsePortPowerLimit.name: rlPethPsePortPowerLimit
rlPethPsePortPowerLimit.description: This variable indicates on the maximum power level in milli watts which is available from rlPethPsePortIndex.

rlPethPsePortStatus.name: rlPethPsePortStatus
rlPethPsePortStatus.description: This variable indicates on the hardware status of rlPethPsePortIndex.

rlPethPsePortTimeRangeName.name: rlPethPsePortTimeRangeName
rlPethPsePortTimeRangeName.description: This variable is used to bind PoE port to time range.

rlPethPsePortOperStatus.name: rlPethPsePortOperStatus
rlPethPsePortOperStatus.description: This Read-Only variable indicates PoE port current status affected by time range active/inactive and admin status.

rlPethMainPseTable.name: rlPethMainPseTable
rlPethMainPseTable.description: The table listing additional read - only information for Power Over Ethernet.

rlPethMainPseGroupIndex.name: rlPethMainPseGroupIndex
rlPethMainPseGroupIndex.description: This variable uniquely identifies the group containing the port to which a power Ethernet PSE is connected. Group means box in the stack, module in a rack and the value 1 MUST be used for non-modular devices. Furthermore, the same value MUST be used in this variable, pethMainPseGroupIndex, and pethNotificationControlGroupIndex to refer to a given box in a stack or module in the rack.

rlPethMainPseSwVersion.name: rlPethMainPseSwVersion
rlPethMainPseSwVersion.description: This variable identifies the MCU SW version.

rlPethMainPseHwVersion.name: rlPethMainPseHwVersion
rlPethMainPseHwVersion.description: This variable identifies the MCU HW version.

rlPethMainPseHwType.name: rlPethMainPseHwType
rlPethMainPseHwType.description: This variable identifies the MCU HW type (enhanced, plus, none).

rlPethMainPsePowerGuardBand.name: rlPethMainPsePowerGuardBand
rlPethMainPsePowerGuardBand.description: This variable identifies the guard band in [W] for not connecting additional ports.

rlPethPowerPseTable.name: rlPethPowerPseTable
rlPethPowerPseTable.description: The table listing additional read-write information for Power Over Ethernet.

rlPethPowerPseGroupIndex.name: rlPethPowerPseGroupIndex
rlPethPowerPseGroupIndex.description: This variable uniquely identifies the group containing the port to which a power Ethernet PSE is connected. Group means box in the stack, module in a rack and the value 1 MUST be used for non-modular devices. rlPethPowerPsePower.name: rlPethPowerPsePower
